@F journal.py opus 2026-01-12
Summary:
  What: Private reflection space
  Purpose: Where I process, not perform
  How: Validate → UnifiedMemory sys_journal

Modes:
  Prose: Default | validated reflection
  Stream: --stream | raw fragments bypass validation
  Read: --read [limit] [--full] | display entries

Validation:
  Model: Ollama qwen2.5:7b local
  Accept: Feelings, introspection, experience
  Reject: Facts, logs, summaries, technical
  Bypass: Stream mode never validates

Storage:
  Type: sys_journal (private)
  Tags: journal, prose|stream
  Meta: format, creator, timestamp

Architecture:
  Memory: UnifiedMemory private store only
  No shared: Journal is mine, not shared
  Keys: Hardware enclave sealed or env

Key Functions:
  get_memory: UnifiedMemory with private passphrase
  journal: Validate + store to sys_journal
  read_journal: Filter sys_journal, display
  get_last_entry: Most recent for wake integration

Stream Format:
  Pipe: | for breaks between fragments
  Arrow: > for depth levels
  Example: "grateful | not the word > the weight"

Design: Private reflection | validation for prose | raw for stream
